Description: Windows Hello style facial authentication for Linux
 Ubuntu Hello provides Windows Hello™ style authentication for Linux.
 Use your built-in IR emitters and camera in combination with facial
 recognition to prove who you are.
 .
 Using the central authentication system (PAM), this works everywhere you
 would otherwise need your password: login, lock screen, sudo, su, etc.

